raw_data.title: IT Support Specialist II
raw_data.description: Responsible for the triage, and resolution of common end-user incidents and service requests via phone, chat, email, deskside support and ticketing systems. Restores service using documented procedures and escalates per SLA.  Answer, log, and triage tickets; resolution for standard issues (account lockouts, password resets, printer/Wi-Fi issues, VPN/client access, basic O365/M365, browser, peripherals).  Perform deskside remediation (imaging, device swaps, break/fix), peripheral installs, and small hardware refreshes; use remote support tools for off-site users.  Assist with patch/upgrade windows and minor project work (pilot deployments, software rollouts, inventory/audit).
